    "body": "# Pull Request\n\n## Description\nThis PR addresses ESLint warnings by removing `console.log` statements, ensuring the codebase adheres to linting standards. It also aims to resolve merge conflicts encountered during the integration attempt into the `main` branch.\n\n## Type of Change\n- [x] Bug fix (non-breaking change which fixes an issue)\n\n## Testing\n- [x] I have tested this change locally\n- [ ] I have added tests for this change\n- [x] All existing tests pass (TypeScript and lint checks passed)\n- [ ] I have tested the build process (Build timed out during verification)\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] My code follows the project's style guidelines\n- [x] I have performed a self-review of my code\n- [ ] I have commented my code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas\n- [ ] I have made corresponding changes to the documentation\n- [x] My changes generate no new warnings\n- [ ] I have added tests that prove my fix is effective or that my feature works\n- [x] New and existing unit tests pass locally with my changes (TypeScript and lint tests passed)\n- [ ] Any dependent changes have been merged and published\n\n## Screenshots (if applicable)\nN/A\n\n## Additional Notes\nThe build process timed out during verification. However, lint and TypeScript checks passed after the changes. This PR also addresses merge conflicts encountered during the integration attempt.\n\n---\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-fe06faa5-8500-4145-9d4d-cbaa14422a55\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-dark.svg\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor-light.svg\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" src=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-cursor.svg\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?id=bc-fe06faa5-8500-4145-9d4d-cbaa14422a55\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/open-in-web-dark.svg\"><source me